{"word":"πληθύνω","slug":"πληθύνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πληϑύνω</el></b> [<el>πληϑύω</el> Ionic form of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πλῆθος\">πλῆθος</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘cause to become more in number’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ tr.\">tr.</a> <b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> <b>increase, multiply <a href='B:540 9:10'>2 Cor 9:10</a>; <a href='B:650 6:14'>Hb 6:14</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <b><a href='B:470 24:12'>Mt 24:12</a>; <a href='B:510 6:7'>Ac 6:7</a>; <a href='B:510 7:17'>7:17</a>; <a href='B:510 9:31'>9:31</a>; <a href='B:510 12:24'>12:24</a>; <a href='B:670 1:2'>1 Pt 1:2</a>; <a href='B:680 1:2'>2 Pt 1:2</a>; Jd 2:2.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘become more in number’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a> <b>increase in number, multiply <a href='B:510 6:1'>Ac 6:1</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:πλῆθος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:πλήκτης\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}